{
  "texts": [
    "Groundedness, the final metric in this category, focuses on determining whether the statements generated by the model align with factual and existing knowledge.",
    "Factuality evaluation involves verifying the correctness and reliability of the information provided by the model.",
    "This assessment requires examining the presence of true-causal relations among generated words 30, which must be supported by evidence from reliable reference sources 7, 12.",
    "Hallucination issues in healthcare chatbots arise when responses appear factually accurate but lack a validity 5, [31] [32] [33].",
    "To address this, groundedness leverages relevant factual information, promoting sound reasoning and staying up-to-date ensuring validity."
  ]
}